## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-197">他們也發現同時搜尋其他結果時，非同步搜尋可以顯示結果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-197">An asynchronous search can show results as they are found while simultaneously searching for additional results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-198">這是適用於工作，例如填入清單方塊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-198">This is useful for tasks such as populating list boxes.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-199">這個屬性的預設設定為 `false`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-199">The default setting for this property is `false`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-200">下列 C# 範例會示範如何建立非同步搜尋。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-200">The following C# example shows how to create an asynchronous search.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
//Set the Asynchronous property to true.  
src.Asynchronous = true;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-204">這個屬性設定為屬性必須是辨別的名稱屬性，例如成員或 managedBy。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-204">The attribute that this property is set to must be a distinguished name attribute, such as member or managedBy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-205">屬性可以是單一或多重值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-205">The attribute can be either single or multi-valued.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-206">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 <<c0> [ 成員](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-member)並[受管理的](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-managedby)文章。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-206">For more information, see the [Member](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-member) and [Managed-By](/windows/desktop/adschema/a-managedby) articles.</span></span>
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-207">執行搜尋的目標由基底物件的屬性中指定的辨別名稱所識別的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-207">The search is performed against the objects that are identified by the distinguished name that is specified in the attribute of the base object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-208">例如，如果基底物件是 adschema 群組類別和<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A>設為 「 成員 」，則會針對群組成員的所有物件會執行搜尋。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-208">For example, if the base object is an adschema group class and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> is set to "member," then the search will be performed against all objects that are members of the group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-209">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 <<c0> [ 分組類別](/windows/desktop/adschema/c-group)文章。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-209">For more information, see the [Group class](/windows/desktop/adschema/c-group) article.</span></span>
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-210">當<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A>使用屬性時，<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A>屬性必須設為<xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-210">When the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property is used, the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property must be set to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-211">如果<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A>屬性設定為任何其他值，設定<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A>屬性將會擲回<xref:System.ArgumentException>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-211">If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property is set to any other value, setting the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property will throw an <xref:System.ArgumentException>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-212">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 <<c0> [ 執行屬性範圍查詢](/windows/desktop/adsi/performing-an-attribute-scoped-query)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-212">For more information, see the [Performing an Attribute Scope Query](/windows/desktop/adsi/performing-an-attribute-scoped-query).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-213">下列範例示範如何使用<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A>屬性與成員屬性，以取得群組的成員。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-213">The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property with the member attribute to get the members of a group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-214">接著它會列印出第一個和最後一個名稱的成員以及電話號碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-214">It then prints out the first and last names of the members and their telephone numbers.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
DirectoryEntry group = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=MyGroup, …");  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher(group "(&(objectClass=user)(objectCategory=Person))");  
src.AttributeScopedQuery = "member";  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("sn");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("givenName");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("telephoneNumber");  
foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll())  
{  
    Console.WriteLine("…");  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-232">下列 C# 範例示範如何設定<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A>屬性設<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always>，如此一來，它在搜尋附屬物件和尋找基底物件時取值別名。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-232">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> property to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> , so that it dereferences aliases when both searching subordinates and locating base objects.</span></span>  
  
```  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
// Set DerefAlias to Always.  
src.DerefAlias = DerefenceAlias.Always;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-242">下列範例示範如何傳回十六進位格式的辨別名稱的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-242">The following example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-303">如果<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A>為 null 參考 (`Nothing` Visual Basic 中)，搜尋根目錄設為您的伺服器目前使用之網域的根目錄。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-303">If <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> is a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), the search root is set to the root of the domain that your server is currently using.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-304">有數種方式可在通用類別目錄中搜尋：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-304">There are several ways to search in the global catalog:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-305">列舉通用類別目錄，並挑選第一個子系。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-305">Enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-306">指定伺服器名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-306">Specify the server name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-307">您可以使用 DsGetDcName 函式來尋找通用類別目錄。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-307">Use the DsGetDcName function to find the global catalog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-308">如需有關 DsGetDcName 函式的詳細資訊，請參閱[DsGetDcName](/windows/desktop/api/dsgetdc/nf-dsgetdc-dsgetdcnamea)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-308">For more information on the DsGetDcName function, see the [DsGetDcName](/windows/desktop/api/dsgetdc/nf-dsgetdc-dsgetdcnamea).</span></span>
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-309">取得 RootDSE 通用類別目錄，並詢問 「 rootNamingContext"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-309">Get the RootDSE  of the global catalog and ask for "rootNamingContext".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-310">使用通用類別目錄，如同使用 LDAP，請指定搜尋路徑。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-310">Use the global catalog, specifying a search path as if using LDAP.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-311">例如，"GC: / / OU =...，DC =...，DC =...」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-311">For example, "GC://OU=..., DC=..., DC=...".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-312">下列 C# 程式碼示範如何列舉通用類別目錄，並挑選第一個子系。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-312">The following C# code shows how to enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
    ```csharp  
    DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("GC://forestname");  
    IEnumerator ie = entry.Children.GetEnumerator();  
    ie.MoveNext();  
    entry = (DirectoryEntry)ie.Current;  
    DirectorySearcher search = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
    ```

  
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.SecurityMasks = SecurityMasks.Dacl | SecurityMasks.Owner;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
