 <span data-ttu-id="b76cb-350">下列 C# 範例示範如何設定<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A>屬性設`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b76cb-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
